</row>
<row>
<entry>The center earns revenues of $10,000, and variable costs are $15,000. The center should shut down now.</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry>
<equation id="ch08mod02_uneq11"><m:math display="block">
 <m:mrow>
  <m:mtable columnalign="left">
   <m:mtr columnalign="left">
    <m:mtd columnalign="left">
     <m:mrow>
      <m:mtext>profit = total revenue </m:mtext><m:mo>–</m:mo><m:mtext> (fixed costs + variable cost)</m:mtext>
